2. If you do want your item, contact Postnord with your order ID and they will release the package free of charge. That means weâ€™ve covered your whole purchase, shipping fees & Postnord VAT for you!

We apologize for any inconvenience and are working round the clock to make sure all 1 million merchants follow Postnord rules in the future!
